        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Chronic Condition Copay Elimination Act</b><br> <br> This bill requires health insurers to cover, without cost sharing, preventive items and services for certain chronic conditions, such as heart disease, diabetes, and asthma, among others.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
